@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">
        Welcome to the HealFoundation
        <img src="/images/heallogo.png" alt="Heal Logo" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; vertical-align: middle;">
    </h1>
</div>

<div class="center-content">
    <p class="lead mt-3" style="text-align: center;">
        The Heal Foundation is an integral organ of the Arya Samaj
        which advances its cause of doing good to the world by promoting the physical, spiritual and
        social welfare of every sentient being. The Arya Samaj subscribes to its famous 10
        Principles of belief in God, benevolence, altruism and the alleviation of the suffering of fellow
        man. These 10 Principles are a blueprint for development of an individual as well as society.
       
    </p>
    <p class="lead mt-4" style="text-align: center;">
        The HEAL Foundation is the official humanitarian wing of the Arya Samaj South Africa with the acronym which stands for:
    </p>
    <p class="lead mt-5" style="text-align: center;">
        H – Humanitarian, E – Enviromental, A – Animal L – Liberation.
    </p>
    

</div>

<!-- Carousel Container -->
<footer class="custom-green-footer">
<div class="carousel-container" style="max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide carousel-fade" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="/images/human.jpg" class="img-fluid w-100" style="border-radius: 20px"  alt="Human">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/images/environmental.jpg" class="img-fluid w-100" style="border-radius: 20px" alt="Enviromental">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Enviromental</h5>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/images/animal.jpg" class="img-fluid w-100" style="border-radius: 20px" alt="Animal liberation">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Animal Liberation</h5>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
    </div>
    </div>

</footer>

<!-- What We Offer Section -->
<section class="features-4">
    <div class="features4-block py-5">
        <div class="container py-lg-4">
            <div class="title-content text-center mb-lg-5 mt-4">
                <h3 class="hny-title">What We Offer</h3>
                <p class="fea-para">
                    To promote the upliftment, welfare and sustainability of the environment and all living beings, thereby ensuring a more harmonious and prosperous society.
                    To provide sustainable activities in the pursuance of the core mandate of the HEAL Foundation, that are delivered compassionately and efficiently, never compromising on values and needs of society, in a fair and impartial manner.

                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="row features4-grids text-center mt-lg-4">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 features4-grid mt-4">
                    <div class="features4-grid-inn">
                        <div class="img-featured move-on-hover">
                            <img src="/images/human.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-circle" alt="Human">
                        </div>
                        <div class="features4-rightinfo">
                            <h5><a href="/Human/Index" class="custom-green-link">Human</a></h5>
                            <p>Serving those in need is one of the highest ideals of being human. Therefore, one of the key objectives of the HEAL Foundation will be to facilitate projects that would serve and uplift the community.  </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 features4-grid mt-4">
                    <div class="features4-grid-inn">
                        <div class="img-featured move-on-hover">
                            <img src="/images/environmental.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-circle" alt="Enviromental">
                        </div>
                        <div class="features4-rightinfo">
                            <h5><a href="/Human/Index" class="custom-green-link">Enviromental</a></h5>
                            <p>The world is currently facing a climate crisis and the onus is on each one of us to start living a more environmentally conscious lifestyle. Therefore, an integral part of the Foundations mandate will be to ensure that the projects carried out are ones that promote the sustainability of the planet.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 features4-grid mt-4">
                    <div class="features4-grid-inn">
                        <div class="img-featured move-on-hover">
                            <img src="/images/animal.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-circle" alt="Animal Liberation">
                        </div>
                        <div class="features4-rightinfo">
                            <h5><a href="/Human/Index" class="custom-green-link">Animal</a></h5>
                            <p>Animal welfare forms part as another integral organ of the Foundation.  Their protection and preservation is paramount in this ever changing environment and therefore all projects initiated by the Foundation are to ensure that the welfare of animals are taken care of.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

       
        <!-- Waves Section -->
        <section class="waves-section">
            <span>
                <svg class="waves" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
                     viewBox="0 24 150 28" preserveAspectRatio="none" shape-rendering="auto">
                    <defs>
                        <path id="gentle-wave" d="M-160 44c30 0 58-18 88-18s 58 18 88 18 58-18 88-18 58 18 88 18 v44h-352z" />
                    </defs>
                    <g class="parallax">
                        <use xlink:href="#gentle-wave" x="48" y="0" fill="rgba(116, 160, 78,0.3)">
                            <animate attributeName="x" from="0" to="48" dur="6s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
                        </use>
                        <use xlink:href="#gentle-wave" x="48" y="5" fill="rgba(116, 160, 78,0.1)">
                            <animate attributeName="x" from="0" to="48" dur="8s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
                        </use>
                        <use xlink:href="#gentle-wave" x="48" y="3" fill="rgba(116, 160, 78,0.2)">
                            <animate attributeName="x" from="0" to="48" dur="10s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
                        </use>
                        <use xlink:href="#gentle-wave" x="48" y="7" fill="rgba(116, 160, 78,0.4)">
                            <animate attributeName="x" from="0" to="48" dur="12s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
                        </use>
                    </g>
                </svg>
            </span>
            <div class="footer__inner">
                <div class="footer__social">
                    <ul class="social-menu"></ul>
                </div>
              
            </div>
            <!-- Privacy Policy Footer -->
            <footer class="text-center mt-5">
                <a href="/Home/Privacy" class="custom-green-link">Privacy Policy</a>

                
            </footer>

        </section>


</section>



<style>

    .custom-green-footer {
        background-color: #74A04E; /* Custom green color */
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 10px; /* Optional: adds rounded corners to the footer */
        max-width: 750px; /* Example max-width */
        margin: 0 auto; /* Center align horizontally */
    }

    .img-featured .rounded-circle {
        border: 2px solid #000; /* Black border around the circular images */
        padding: 5px; /* Optional: Adds padding around the images */
    }
    .move-on-hover img {
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

        .move-on-hover img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }


    .custom-green-link {
        background-color: #74A04E; /* Custom green color */
        border-color: #74A04E; /* Custom green border color */
        color: white; /* Text color */
        padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem; /* Button padding */
        font-size: 1rem; /* Button font size */
        border-radius: 0.25rem; /* Button border radius */
        text-align: center; /* Center text */
        display: inline-block; /* Inline block display */
        text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline */
    }

        .custom-green-link:hover {
            background-color: #74A04E; /* Darker green on hover */
            border-color: #74A04E; /* Darker green border on hover */
            color: white; /* Ensure text color stays white */
        }

   
    .social-media-links--platforms {
        list-style-type: none; /* Removes bullet points */
        padding: 0; /* Removes default padding */
        margin: 0; /* Removes default margin */
    }

    /* Style for the waves section */
    .waves-section {
        position: relative;
        height: 50vh; /* Height set to half the viewport */
        overflow: hidden; /* Ensures no overflow */
        background-color: #ffffff; /* Background color behind the waves */
    }

    .waves {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%; /* Make the waves take up the full height of the section */
    }


</style>

